<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-07 00:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8538 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBA-MODESTI-COLUMN-LA     04-07 0785
