   FOOD
</P>
<P>
   COXNET FOOD 0406 _ Savory tarts are a supreme way to celebrate
spring. And tarts _ or tortas _ are so versatile, you can tinker
with most recipes to include your favorite vegetables, cheeses and
meats. Sliced thin and small, they work well as appetizers or side
dishes. Make heartier cuts and pair with a salad for a main meal.
Walker, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art includes one 4-column
color photo of a tart.
