impressionist artist is that he was also a foodie. Throughout the
exhibit Park 75 restaurant will be featuring Monet's luncheons and
we have created a menu based upon recipes in a cookbook by a family
member who researched the meals he feasted on. (Walker, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) WITH COLOR PHOTO.
