be a wine expert?'' ``How old are you, anyway?'' ``Hey, are you
sure you're old enough to drink?'' Sweeney, believed to be the lone
sommelier between the Culinary Institute of America and Montreal,
is a mere 29 years old. By DOUG BLACKBURN.
