<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-07 13:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9079 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ISRAEL-HIGH-TECH-BOS &LR;      04-07 1326
