<SLUG> BC-HISPANIC-PHOTOS08-1STLEDE-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    TRAVELING PHOTO EXHIBIT SHOWS DIVERSITY OF AMERICAN HISPANICS
 &HT;    Eds: Adds dates of Texas visits in 6th graf.
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (l) lifestyle categories.
