<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-07 15:37 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9205 &Cx1f; tth-z
a b &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-PARKINSON'S-DISEASE-S     04-07 2232
