</P>
<P>
   CIR-RESEARCH-LIBRARY (Undated) _ Research libraries meet the
electronic future. How to store digital information, who owns it,
how will it be read in the future. By Katie Hafner.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   And
</P>
<P>
