<HEADLINE>
THE DURABILITY DERBY
</HEADLINE>
 
(EDS: Accompanies TV-PERKINS-COLUMN) (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   How other long-running shows rank _ and whether it's time for
them to bag it:
</P>
