</P>
<P>
   Network: CBS
</P>
<P>
   Seasons: 5
</P>
<P>
   Critical status: Remains a perfect fit for Sunday nights.
</P>
<P>
   _
</P>
<P>
   _ Ken Parish Perkins
</P>
