<P>
   UNDATED _ I'd been figuring that the hard-core baseball
boycotters had washed their hands of me and that the nonboycotters
were tired of my ambivalence _ to boycott or not to boycott, that
is the question _ and so I wasn't counting on much of a response to
last week's pre-season baseball column. It was definitely a
pleasant surprise when I received a supportive e-mail from a reader
who shares my love/disgust relationship with big-league baseball.
By BILL THOMPSON. Story has moved in ``k'' commentary category. &QL; 
