<P>
   AARON ANNIVERSARY
</P>
<P>
   Cox News Service is marking the 25th anniversary of Hank Aaron's
breaking of the home run mark with a package of stories and photos.
Aaron hit his 715th home run in Atlanta on April 8, 1974, to break
Babe Ruth's record.
</P>
<P>
   Two photos, one a new color portrait of Aaron and the other
showing him circling the bases after the record home run, are
available on the Cox server.
