 Wednesday, April 7, 1999    
 Editors     
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service has filed or will file the following
stories for Thursday and Sunday. If you have questions, please call
Susie McBee or Tim Spence at 202-298-6920. For questions about
Houston Chronicle sports stories, please call 713-220-7896.
