citizens. But, I'm confused by all the politicians _ from President
Clinton on down _ who want us to think of Yugoslav President
Slobodan Milosevic as another Hitler. In this age of squeamish
politicians and skittish citizens, there seems to be an unwritten
rule that we must convince ourselves a miscreant has risen to
