News, someone posted a fake news story that said an American
technology company called PairGain Technologies Inc. was being
taken over by an Israeli rival. The report spread to a Yahoo
message board and then to other sites frequented by stock traders,
who quickly bid up PairGain's stock by more than 30 percent. By
